description:
(Part 4 of 6 - Ron Kelly) Soon no man might buy or sell, save he that had the mark (Revelation 13:17). Are you ready for the mark of the beast? What will happen when it is enforced? What must we know, and do, during that crisis hour? Discover inspirational, hopeful, practical answers by watching these presentations!
